  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/0e9608f1b65b8da96b9ae460474b4402.poster.avif?t=1756418146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/0e9608f1b65b8da96b9ae460474b4402.webm?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/0e9608f1b65b8da96b9ae460474b4402.mp4?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>How would you feel about being trapped on the moon while everyone and everything is trying to kill you? How would you feel if your only friend betrayed you?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/dc50daca2061ea2e155c4a068cbb9e45.poster.avif?t=1756418146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/dc50daca2061ea2e155c4a068cbb9e45.webm?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/dc50daca2061ea2e155c4a068cbb9e45.mp4?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Try not to die while exploring the secret facility located on the Moon and solve various tests using experimental technology to defy all odds and escape.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/ef35285c8b53e263bb999b05b3f0c2a7.poster.avif?t=1756418146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/ef35285c8b53e263bb999b05b3f0c2a7.webm?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/ef35285c8b53e263bb999b05b3f0c2a7.mp4?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But don't lose all hope. Someone out there still believes in you.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Singleplayer - Story Mode<br></li><li>Physics based puzzles<br></li><li>Microphone usage<br></li><li>75 levels</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/0e9608f1b65b8da96b9ae460474b4402.poster.avif?t=1756418146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/0e9608f1b65b8da96b9ae460474b4402.webm?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/0e9608f1b65b8da96b9ae460474b4402.mp4?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>How would you feel about being trapped on the moon while everyone and everything is trying to kill you? How would you feel if your only friend betrayed you?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/dc50daca2061ea2e155c4a068cbb9e45.poster.avif?t=1756418146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/dc50daca2061ea2e155c4a068cbb9e45.webm?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/dc50daca2061ea2e155c4a068cbb9e45.mp4?t=1756418146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Try not to die while exploring the secret facility located on the Moon and solve various tests using experimental technology to defy all odds and escape.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/ef35285c8b53e263bb999b05b3f0c2a7.poster.avif?t=1756418146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463360/extras/ef35285c8b53e263bb999b05b3f0c2a7.webm?t=17564181